[I] A library to use TrueType fonts in SDL applications

[T] This is a sample library which allows you to use TrueType fonts in
[T] your SDL applications. It comes with an example program "showfont"
[T] which displays an example string for a given TrueType font file.

[U] https://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/

